    dc:description "Fig. 48. Distribution of Begonia sect. Eupetalum (Lindl.) A.DC. in Peru and surrounding countries. A. B. geraniifolia Hook. (red) and B. joshii Moonlight (blue). B. B. neoharlingii L.B.Sm. & Wassh. (red) and B. weberbaueri Irmsch. (blue). Black lines indicate country borders, grey lines indicate major administrative divisions, blue lines indicate rivers, and shading indicates elevation." ;
